      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><span>The following issue may compromise the security of your Liferay Digital Experience Platform (DXP) implementation. This notification provides a description of the latest security vulnerability and recommended actions for Liferay Subscribers.</span></p>\n<h2 align=\"left\">Affected Version/s</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Liferay Digital Experience Platform 7.4</li>\n<li>Liferay Digital Experience Platform 7.3</li>\n<li>Liferay Digital Experience Platform 7.2</li>\n<li>Liferay Digital Experience Platform 7.1</li>\n<li>Liferay Digital Experience Platform 7.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 align=\"left\">Vulnerability Information</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/5327046151949\" target=\"_self\">LSV-980</a>: LDAP credentials exposed in URL</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 align=\"left\">Download</h2>\n<p>The listed vulnerabilities will be fixed under DXP Security Fix Pack: 202201. DXP Security Fix Packs require the latest released Fix Pack or can be built on a specific Fix Pack level<span> </span><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360035038331-DXP-Security-Fix-Packs#h_be07a4b8-d1fe-4b98-ad08-2a6af0797283\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://discover.liferay.com/e2t/tc/VX9Rly1Y5G7MW64Q2j0679HSqW6TYKFS49CJJTN1YBnvN3lGnpV1-WJV7CgPq3W23xcXc1Tq0MfW7ghjj_6vqffsN40Yt0cHCbfVW1gGF-F5yFxl3W66GqcJ5LyHWKW4pcsJR5W_hlvW7v60gc81vPYfN5H_Ydgmp4JhW5bX9sm9gGHG-W6Ffx2V5bzx6gW9bCmsw5bhSmXW3_Zfrp5yHzSPW1LhL4Q7Mtc_bW3NVxgT7x84W5W6WYs0M6xZrj_W377Ph12Q0DWYW8PVTVJ56cGBqW724gfT5sjRqZVq8WyK22HkJ9W2yhLQk8CTxmHW3NcKfM8Vf3vsW79bYDS5g-GDQW8nt9S_4CvS9qN6M4BPFV0420W8pbFSw34sWNxW8bd5z91NDYy13mfq1&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1649264831845000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2QuuqOrBebJFLtYBjv3jdN\">upon request</a>. Please read the<span> </span><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360035038331-DXP-Security-Fix-Packs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://discover.liferay.com/e2t/tc/VX9Rly1Y5G7MW64Q2j0679HSqW6TYKFS49CJJTN1YBnv93lGmQV1-WJV7CgDV7V5nLJB2Qg1QgW2tZNs_1BLMTfW5m5-Kr2_95XPN1CzvvHVTB0QW73hvFr89LhNsW3kQrqZ8bBtDLVJrc_m8zqCPzW4rvpV3395qjyVPs7Y392CrG1W8Mt-n3867drZW1SJWz59fk-CsVdcLVH3zY0w1W17njnB1F1hS7W6yWtcY6w7lhrV9Ylb44f6s9_V1YV-D8qzDYZW31bBtS7g9t61TDQCr1ZVK9-W7qlBf45Y55kYW4yqqgl3X69dXW4mXjXg54Wqg1VZky1v3rTpd439HY1&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1649264831845000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2ZHxTJ0SZbVKLXxNiZ1Y4v\">DXP Security Fix Packs</a><span> </span>article for more information and installation instructions.</p>\n<p>For more information on the vulnerability and affected versions for the issue, please visit the<span> </span><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360018875952\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://discover.liferay.com/e2t/tc/VX9Rly1Y5G7MW64Q2j0679HSqW6TYKFS49CJJTN1YBnv93lGmQV1-WJV7CgG4-W3R8v_K4ndZ_BW6gHbkf91FsK6W5KbdZ98fD475W6h2R4710QbgxW5JnQ0R11RZm9W6-Z4VT4x_ySNW4vVzyn31_xRfW7kWGyZ6HS3sgW2h2zLN3JhxTHW133x9z8g6p3jW2vT_P03dQWBJW5F2c3f8XgPCfVdVBc39475dkW2yjBYB6S-1dnW3Tt0Z050gnJWW8WLF8g76_t0QW7V2JBq63DqM8VflJDx2tZdGtW7m8kFF5yTbmJVwq8gw4HwsMbW9gJs_f8PrPStW3Rrcts93Bjdy3jZT1&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1649264831845000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0OWeWH8oroW1VKUNQEwcy9\">Help Center Security Advisories</a><span> </span>page.</p>"
      },
